rc=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d327ac83f9d6bf158ad2eac2f142e2ebce1af8b","tid":1312893,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"槍口對外"},{"pid":"a26cb9d57c42cac499cd31c086d66ba439addd08","tid":1312893,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811175d4cc6c680d25793f3d873bfe2cb2f0192a","tid":1312893,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"【#警察濫暴 #必須廣傳 #請廣傳】<br />\n<br />\n7月13日 上水 晚上<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察在大致完成清場行動後，在天橋上無故發難，突然大叫且追向一名16歲青年。青年受驚立刻拔腿就跑，最終被迫跳橋避開警察！<br />\n<br />\n幸好當時有社工及攝影師將青年拉住，青年方可無礙。但警察隨即趕到將青年拉上橋並立刻逮捕，控以「非法集會」。<br />\n<br />\n本專頁強調，及時救回青年的是社工和攝影師，並非後來趕至的警察；警察只是在攝影師將青年拉住後，將青年拉回橋上拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警察暴行實在罄竹難書。香港人根本無法制衡警暴，但又必須自救！請各位將黑警惡行，用一切可行方式公諸於世！"},{"pid":"71b5b0a3b5cb7a23ad8444d3b9e7b8852efdf350","tid":1312893,"uid":199590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f6639727bf72a0391c79796e891f2c01f0e7ffd5","tid":1312893,"uid":54748,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"如果人地講事實都要批鬥咁連登仔真係惡過共產黨架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"呢度不嬲唔俾講事實喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一講就話&ldquo;躝啦 波台狗&rdquo; &ldquo;好多3毛撥冷水&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ac7df9b8c38a096a9f454546647a40a24539e3db","tid":1312893,"uid":57185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"push. we connect"},{"pid":"15c27582e311d4562df72e5f081016bf64529b6c","tid":1312893,"uid":264641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79b24387b203d130dd8916845189a3ee577c5b37","tid":1312893,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3351dd8